Request for Public Input  

The Charlotte County Board of Supervisors has recently developed a draft strategic plan which includes goals, objectives & actions to guide operational and policy decisions. The Board would like to encourage citizens to review the draft plan and provide feedback.  

The plan may be viewed here. Hardcopies are also available at the County Administration Office, 250 LeGrande Avenue, Suite A, P.O. Box 608, Charlotte Court House, VA  23923.  Comments can be submitted to the Administration Office or by e-mailing melder@charlotteva.com.

The Board of Supervisors will be seeking input through April 30, 2019.
